text: Adam Kappacher (born 15 December 1993) is an Austrian freestyle skier. He competed in the 2017 FIS Freestyle World Ski Championships, and in the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian male freestyle skiers Category:Olympic freestyle skiers of Austria Category:Freestyle skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics
